name: The Dead Shall Serve
text: When you set this scheme in motion, for each opponent, put up to one target creature card from that player's graveyard onto the battlefield under your control. Each of those creatures attacks its owner each combat if able.

editions.flavor: "Tell your old master I said hello."

name: The Eon Fog
text:
Players skip their untap steps.
Whenever you roll {CHAOS}, untap all permanents you control.

name: The Fallen
text: At the beginning of your upkeep, The Fallen deals 1 damage to each opponent it has dealt damage to this game.

editions.flavor: Magic often masters those who cannot master it.

name: The Fallen Apart
text:
The Fallen Apart comes into play with two arms and two legs.
Whenever damage is dealt to The Fallen Apart, remove an arm or a leg from it.
The Fallen Apart can't attack if it has no legs and can't block if it has no arms.
